# Ejemplo Ilustrativo 5.1 - Grid Frame | Mario Paz
> <hr/>
> Structural Dynamics - Theory and Computation, Chapter 5
> For the grid frame shown in Figure 5.4, perform the structural analysis to determine:
> (a) Displacements at the joints between elements
> (b) End forces on the elements
> (c) Reactions of the supports

@{draw 600 400}
# Fig. 5.4 Grid frame for Illustrative Example 5.1
